{"tid":1392121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話00後好奶共，依家係抗共主力","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T17:06:30.000Z","uid":33307,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"517282541c3c7471b84d8e9c9de8caf8af0699ac","tid":1392121,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2feeda973958e305b73b10c49472f08dcd49f58a","tid":1392121,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月3日 旺角遊行<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"7b7bd65106aa2bc3d2222839d51a7772d87a740f","tid":1392121,"uid":6528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年內落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年內！"},{"pid":"5830e4f26b07d5e255942dd3bcda53bd83d65a74","tid":1392121,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔係咪收錯風"},{"pid":"72fa1ae075807d89883d1b3a253cb197d6f03232","tid":1392121,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"517282541c3c7471b84d8e9c9de8caf8af0699ac","tid":1392121,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:46:54.000Z","msg":"奶共嗰批冇出嚟發夢 唔代表唔存在"},{"pid":"04e351f04e65413691eb9e84f759a3edf780e264","tid":1392121,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"8d51a5845a1275d3d89d7104d63248a19b502259","tid":1392121,"uid":131282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:47:56.000Z","msg":"三毛搞分化 搞世代之爭"},{"pid":"2432d79b0e6ef10a2af9e778f8d33f73