"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d51a5845a1275d3d89d7104d63248a19b502259","tid":1392121,"uid":131282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:47:56.000Z","msg":"三毛搞分化 搞世代之爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"分化社會再自相殘殺<br />\n<br />\n廢青廢老<br />\n港男港女<br />\nXX後<br />\n<br />\n今次其實破曬功，我哋連某啲藍絲都connect 到<br />\n<br />\n中立犬儒嘅就算，冇行動力影響力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"叫抗爭者做小朋友都係分化既一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地勇敢 敢於承擔所以出黎 係大人既表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509a93ee15e4db27b5b198787e0d008cf50aba8a","tid":1392121,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42eec43fd8c82079edace7a8676f8f045ccdd833","tid":1392121,"uid":182994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:52:09.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得新世代好靈活<br />\n完全體現到食窮民建聯 票投本民前既精神<br />\n啲表弟表妹讀中學一見到大陸科水既交流團全部9衝<br />\n但係都好撚反共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:45:20.000Z","msg":"醒目仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有著數就r到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過大陸交流團都係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acce53dc3a82fcfe671ad56b634d2a0524b3014b","tid":1392121,"uid":266878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"樓主啱，不過，00後之前比人覺得奶共係因為佢地好奶大陸文化，呢下洗腦好毒，當你慣左嗰種文化，你好難去同佢切割，所以，聽我呢個廢老講，從今以後要主動抗拒劣質文化，即係話：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔玩大陸game, 唔用大陸電話，唔講大陸term, 唔睇大陸劇，唔追大陸星，唔飲喜茶，唔好得閒就返深圳扮文青，唔好成日開口埋口叫內地，叫大陸</span></span><br />\n<br />\n文化係洗腦嘅最佳武器，劣質文化係劣質政權嘅最佳武器<br />\n<br />\n咁，如果有啲00後話以前成日玩開大陸嘢搣甩晒會悶𨶙到閪咁咁點算。 講真，而家大家都知歐美嘅重要性，歐美日文化博大精深優質多元，仲有，記住練英文練英文練英文!<br />\n<br />\n搣甩衰嘢，如果唔係你老左就可能變左屯門公園啲阿伯中意睇大媽歌，唔好忘記啲阿伯後生時都係中共文化浸大的"},{"pid":"181873077ce1b481bdd2d290070ace534ca1c99a","tid":1392121,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=e4b54233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"cf8860a85e0aab595225f2172a560fb44489dab6","tid":1392121,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月3日 旺角遊行<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"6218a93c3bb8a64905e6f54404a991268783a0a4","tid":1392121,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要說&quot;推&quot;, <br />\n<br />\n試著用hashtag：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">感謝靚聲絲打讀出 hashtag 無限loop</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-612048585/loop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-612048585%2Floop&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=cc3331eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-612048585/loop</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hf7ppz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%